<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lucca | 商务运营与大型活动策划专家</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-primary: #fafafa;
            --bg-secondary: #ffffff;
            --text-primary: #0a0a0a;
            --text-secondary: #525252;
            --text-muted: #737373;
            --accent: #0a0a0a;
            --border: #e5e5e5;
            --tag-bg: #f5f5f5;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
            max-width: 1200px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 
                0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
                inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            z-index: 1000;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 64px;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .nav-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .nav-contact {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .btn-contact {
            background: var(--text-primary);
            color: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-contact:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Ambient Background */
        .ambient-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        .ambient-blob {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.4;
            animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .ambient-blob:nth-child(1) {
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8e6cf, #88d8b0);
            top: -10%;
            left: -10%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
            animation-duration: 25s;
        }

        .ambient-blob:nth-child(2) {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd3b6, #ffaaa5);
            top: 50%;
            right: -10%;
            animation-delay: -5s;
            animation-duration: 20s;
        }

        .ambient-blob:nth-child(3) {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcedc1, #a8e6cf);
            bottom: -10%;
            left: 30%;
            animation-delay: -10s;
            animation-duration: 22s;
        }

        .ambient-blob:nth-child(4) {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c3bef7, #a8b4f0);
            top: 20%;
            right: 30%;
            animation-delay: -15s;
            animation-duration: 18s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            25% { transform: translate(50px, -30px) scale(1.05); }
            50% { transform: translate(-20px, 40px) scale(0.95); }
            75% { transform: translate(-40px, -20px) scale(1.02); }
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 100px 5% 40px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        /* Typewriter Effect */
        .typewriter-container {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            min-height: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .typewriter-text {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .typewriter-cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 3px;
            height: 1.4em;
            background-color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-left: 2px;
            vertical-align: text-bottom;
            animation: cursor-blink 0.8s step-end infinite;
        }

        @keyframes cursor-blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        .hero-content .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            max-width: 500px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Parallax Elements */
        .parallax-layer {
            will-change: transform;
            transition: transform 0.1s linear;
        }

        .parallax-slow {
            transform: translateY(calc(var(--scroll) * -0.3px));
        }

        .parallax-medium {
            transform: translateY(calc(var(--scroll) * -0.5px));
        }

        .parallax-fast {
            transform: translateY(calc(var(--scroll) * -0.8px));
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .stat {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .hero-image {
            flex: 0.7;
            max-width: 350px;
        }

        .hero-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 16px;
            object-fit: cover;
            aspect-ratio: 3/4;
        }

        /* Section Styles */
        section {
            padding: 80px 5%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        section:first-of-type {
            padding-top: 0;
        }

        .section-header {
            margin-bottom: 64px;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .section-header .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Work Experience Cards */
        .experience-card {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .experience-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .experience-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .experience-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .experience-company {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .experience-period {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            background: var(--tag-bg);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 100px;
        }

        .experience-highlights {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .highlight-item {
            padding: 24px;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .highlight-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .highlight-item h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .highlight-item p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Project Gallery */
        .project-gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .project-card {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 16/10;
            background: var(--border);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .project-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .project-card:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .project-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
            color: white;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .project-card:hover .project-overlay {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Vertical Poster Gallery */
        .poster-gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .poster-card {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 3/4;
            background: var(--border);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .poster-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .poster-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .poster-card:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .poster-card .project-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
            color: white;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .poster-card:hover .project-overlay {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .project-overlay h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-text h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .tag {
            background: var(--tag-bg);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .about-images {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .about-images img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact-section {
            background: var(--text-primary);
            color: var(--bg-primary);
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 80px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 80px 5%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .contact-section h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .contact-section p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .contact-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .contact-links a {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .contact-links a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 5%;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        /* Animations */
        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
        }

        .fade-in.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding-top: 120px;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .hero-stats {
                gap: 32px;
            }

            .hero-image {
                order: -1;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .hero-image img {
                aspect-ratio: 1/1;
            }

            .experience-card {
                padding: 32px;
            }

            .about-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .about-images {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .about-images img {
                height: 250px;
            }

            .poster-gallery {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .contact-section {
                padding: 48px 24px;
                margin: 40px 5%;
            }

            section {
                padding: 60px 5%;
            }

            /* Mobile navigation adjustments */
            nav {
                top: 10px;
                width: calc(100% - 20px);
            }

            .nav-inner {
                height: 56px;
                padding: 0 16px;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .nav-avatar {
                width: 32px;
                height: 32px;
            }

            .btn-contact {
                padding: 8px 16px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Ambient Background -->
    <div class="ambient-bg">
        <div class="ambient-blob"></div>
        <div class="ambient-blob"></div>
        <div class="ambient-blob"></div>
        <div class="ambient-blob"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <img src="lucca个人头像照片.jpg" alt="Lucca" class="nav-avatar">
                Lucca
            </a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#work">工作经历</a>
                <a href="#projects">项目作品</a>
                <a href="#about">关于我</a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-contact">
                <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="btn-contact">联系我</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content fade-in">
            <h1 class="parallax-layer parallax-slow">Hi, 我是 Lucca</h1>
            <div class="typewriter-container">
                <span class="typewriter-text"></span><span class="typewriter-cursor"></span>
            </div>
            <p class="subtitle parallax-layer parallax-slow">在理性的商业数据与感性的体验设计之间，我负责搭建桥梁。拥有操盘 3.1 亿次播放量文旅项目的经验，目前在大理旅居。</p>
            <div class="hero-stats parallax-layer parallax-medium">
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">3.1亿+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">项目播放量</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">5000+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">峰会与会人数</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">7年+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">行业经验</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image fade-in parallax-layer parallax-fast">
            <img src="lucca个人生活照片.jpg" alt="Lucca 在大理">
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Work Experience -->
    <section id="work">
        <div class="section-header fade-in">
            <h2>工作经历</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">从大型文旅项目到 Web3 投研，跨界探索的每一步</p>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-card fade-in">
            <div class="experience-header">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="experience-title">投研分析师 & KOL 运营</h3>
                    <p class="experience-company">海南文鸣互联网科技</p>
                </div>
                <span class="experience-period">2021.07 - 至今</span>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-highlights">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>投研与套利模型</h4>
                    <p>调研市场各种项目，全网首发 StepN 小鞋子套利模型，掀起套利浪潮</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>KOL 影响力运营</h4>
                    <p>以"草莓牛奶"IP 输出长文与视频，全网积累 20k+ 粉丝</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>高净值社区主理</h4>
                    <p>运营"暴躁兔"社区，沉淀 3000+ 用户，服务 150+ 核心付费会员</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>头部机构合作</h4>
                    <p>作为 Huobi、FTX、BNB Chain、EOS 等一线交易所特邀直播嘉宾</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-card fade-in">
            <div class="experience-header">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="experience-title">项目总监</h3>
                    <p class="experience-company">万博文旅（北京）运营管理有限公司</p>
                </div>
                <span class="experience-period">2019.02 - 2021.06</span>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-highlights">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>现象级造节操盘</h4>
                    <p>操盘武汉东湖樱花季，联动抖音打造热门话题，斩获 3.1 亿次播放量</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>大型展馆视觉空间</h4>
                    <p>负责遂宁市宋瓷博物馆、哈尔滨电机厂企业馆等升级改造</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>商业体验与文创</h4>
                    <p>策划"蛋蛋攻略"潮玩阵列，与宜信财富、雀巢合作定制文创周边</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>团队与媒体统筹</h4>
                    <p>从 0 搭建 11 人核心团队，项目累计获得 70+ 家媒体报道</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-card fade-in">
            <div class="experience-header">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="experience-title">策划部负责人</h3>
                    <p class="experience-company">杭州雷鹿科技有限公司</p>
                </div>
                <span class="experience-period">2018.04 - 2018.12</span>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-highlights">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>大型国际峰会策划</h4>
                    <p>负责 2018 全球区块链高峰论坛（菲律宾马尼拉，与会 5000 人）整体策划</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>核心嘉宾组统筹</h4>
                    <p>担任 GBLS 杭州峰会（与会 20000 人）嘉宾组负责人，与杭州市政府联合举办</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>教育项目操盘</h4>
                    <p>统筹"雷鹿大学"项目，线上线下培训两万人</p>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <h4>核心媒体公关</h4>
                    <p>负责媒体对外事宜，与行业头部媒体建立深度战略合作关系</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Projects Section -->
    <section id="projects">
        <div class="section-header fade-in">
            <h2>项目作品</h2>
